nodes.text: Enhanced Battle of Naboo is an expansion card set of the Young Jedi Collectible Card Game, produced by Decipher. The set is based on the original Battle of Naboo set. Contains cards from various scenes in the movie. As with Enhanced Menace of Darth Maul, this set comes with booster packs of Battle of Naboo (YJCCG).
This set has 12 cards, six light side and six dark side.
